description:
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contracted Physiotherapists – Frailty Department&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Located within King’s College Hospital Frailty Department&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for Band 7 Frailty Practioners to join our Bank.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To be considered for these roles, you will need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least six months NHS experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to work on weekends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Availability to work a mixture of 8AM-4PM and 12PM-8PM.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HCPC registration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated and committed, ‘can do’ attitude to work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills, both written and verbal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why chose King’s Staff Bank? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&quot;The people here are very friendly and have made me so welcome and part of their team. I have learnt more than I could ever imagine - the Trust has supported me in my practice and development. I feel so privileged and proud to work at King’s&quot;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for a flexible work pattern, one that complements your current lifestyle?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bank Partners allows you to have control over your work, providing you with a self-booking shift system and access to multiple sites.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our success starts with a team of committed workers. In return for your service, our benefits include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This job operates with a regular line of flexible work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to gain invaluable knowledge and experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working within a diverse and rewarding environment that prioritises both patients and staff wellbeing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First opportunity for work placements before agency staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive pay rates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to free core Bank Partners training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated booking consultant available to assist with any queries and advise on suitable assignments tailored to you&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Electronic timesheet system with weekly payroll and self-booking shift system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to start your journey with Bank Partners? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please apply directly to this advertisement, for further information on the roles please contact the King’s Staff Bank Recruitment Team on Join.KingsBank@bankpartners.co.uk&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
